  "title": "Sales Engineer (Marine Valve/ Woodlands)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Basic <strong>$3,000 - $4,000 + ($500 - $1000) Transport Allowance + Commission</strong></li>\n  <li>Mon - Fri 8.00am - 5.00pm</li>\n  <li>Location: Woodlands</li>\n  <li>Permanent Role + AWS + VB</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and manage projects and sales opportunities to drive revenue growth.</li>\n  <li>Develop and maintain new and existing customer accounts.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and deliver technical presentations to clients.</li>\n  <li>Understand customer needs and competitor activities to develop winning strategies.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with sales support and application engineers.</li>\n  <li>Provide sales and first-level technical support for inquiries and issues.</li>\n  <li>Prepare quotations, proposals, and manage project sales reports.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>1–2 years of relevant experience preferred; Entry-level candidates welcome.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Only shortlisted candidates would be notified</em></p>\n<p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752</p>\n<p>EA. Registration No.: R22111807 | Yap Teng Hui</p>",
